---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="申请指南">
  <section class="pt-20 pb-20 px-4 md:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-center mb-12">申请指南</h1>

      <!-- 申请流程概览 -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="mb-8">申请流程概览</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <div class="apple-card text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold gradient-text mb-2">1</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">准备阶段</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">选校、准备考试成绩</p>
          </div>
          <div class="apple-card text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold gradient-text mb-2">2</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">申请材料</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">准备文书、推荐信</p>
          </div>
          <div class="apple-card text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold gradient-text mb-2">3</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">提交申请</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">通过官方渠道提交</p>
          </div>
          <div class="apple-card text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold gradient-text mb-2">4</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">录取决定</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">等待录取结果</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 详细指南卡片 -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="apple-card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">✍️ 文书撰写指南</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            申请文书是展示你个性和能力的重要机会。我们为你提供详细的文书撰写技巧...
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="inline-block text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-semibold">阅读详情 →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="apple-card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">📋 标化考试要求</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            了解各大学对 SAT、ACT、GRE、GMAT 等标化考试的具体要求...
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="inline-block text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-semibold">阅读详情 →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="apple-card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">🎓 本科申请指南</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            从高中到大学的完整申请流程、时间规划和注意事项...
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="inline-block text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-semibold">阅读详情 →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="apple-card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">👨‍🎓 研究生申请指南</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            硕士和博士项目的申请要求、套磁邮件等专业指导...
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="inline-block text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-semibold">阅读详情 →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="apple-card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">🌍 国际生录取要求</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            国际学生申请需要注意的特殊要求、签证等问题...
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="inline-block text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-semibold">阅读详情 →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="apple-card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">💰 奖学金申请</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            各大学奖学金类型、金额、申请流程和技巧...
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="inline-block text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-semibold">阅读详情 →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 常见问题 -->
      <div class="mt-16">
        <h2 class="mb-8">常见问题 (FAQ)</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <details class="apple-card">
            <summary class="font-bold cursor-pointer">申请需要准备多久？</summary>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">一般建议提前1-2年开始准备申请材料和参加标化考试...</p>
          </details>
          <details class="apple-card">
            <summary class="font-bold cursor-pointer">需要参加哪些考试？</summary>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">本科通常需要 SAT 或 ACT，研究生需要 GRE 或 GMAT...</p>
          </details>
          <details class="apple-card">
            <summary class="font-bold cursor-pointer">如何获得推荐信？</summary>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">通常需要向教授或雇主请求推荐信，提前3-4周通知...</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
